### Register
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

### Send Email Verification Code
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/verify-email/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com"
}

### Confirm Email Verification
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/verify-email/confirm?code=123456
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com"
}

### Send Password Reset Code
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/reset-password/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com"
}

### Confirm Password Reset
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/reset-password/confirm?code=123456&newPassword=NewTest1234!
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com"
}

### Logout
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>
